As a Product Designer at Figma, you will own real impactful projects and take them from ideation to execution. You will work fluidly and collaboratively with the rest of the design team, as well as other functions. Because of this, you should have a broad set of design skills and be motivated to learn. 

This role will be based out of our San Francisco or New York hub.

